{"tid":819058,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"時代告終！福士經典甲蟲車明年停產","createTime":"2018-09-14T13:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T12:43:31.000Z","uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ddf398eb7f410aed78ec2b616babc1ea76c660dd","tid":819058,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:45:44.000Z","msg":"外媒報道，德國福士汽車(Volkswagen)宣布，將於2019年停產甲蟲車(Beetle)。在停產前，公司將在美國推出Final Edition SE及Final Edition SEL兩款特別版。<br />\n<br />\n甲蟲車是福士首款生產的車型，是汽車史上最長壽及最暢銷的車型之一，全球銷量達2,270萬輛。不過，近年小型汽車的銷量持續下滑，今年首8個月，在美國只售出11,151輛，按年跌逾2%。<br />\n<br />\n甲蟲車於1936年完成首次測試，在1938年由納粹德國領袖希特拉批准生產。汽車設計者是保時捷創辦人Ferdinand Porsche，為生產這款車成立了一家汽車廠，亦即現時的福士。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180914/bkn-20180914124804487-0914_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180914%2Fbkn-20180914124804487-0914_00842_001.html&d=jtxzMWEAjToVXpklrv0%2FEzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=3f9029e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180914/bkn-20180914124804487-0914_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a647cf5936f7100f22c766052da5d50b10b3e5","tid":819058,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:47:39.000Z","msg":"香港有幾多架行緊"},{"pid":"766ba68fbd5ebcc56f6949a00c7d5362c372e95a","tid":819058,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b6a647cf5936f7100f22c766052da5d50b10b3e5","tid":819058,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:47:39.000Z","msg":"香港有幾多架行緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:53:48.000Z","msg":"已經好少見, mini cooper最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde4a39b3cdeb9e2b38c574154c0a7779f4ee296","tid":819058,"uid":195215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6a647cf5936f7100